"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/42618","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2014-03-17","<p /> <p /> <p>While the majority of the legacy caseload will move to Universal Credit during 2016 and 2017, claimants in receipt of Income based Employment and Support Allowance (ESA) will retain their current arrangements during this period unless there is a relevant change in their circumstances. Final decisions on the implementation of the programme will be informed by the development of the enhanced digital solution.</p>","Wirral West","Esther McVey","191508 ; 191509","2014-03-17T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/42618/answer","Biography information for Esther McVey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/42618/answer",,,,,"29",,,"2014-03-11",,"1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, whether the Universal Credit system will accept new claims for employment and support allowance by the end of 2016.","false","Biography information for Rachel Reeves","Leeds West","Rachel Reeves","191507"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/42619","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2014-03-17","<p /> <p /> <p>While the majority of the legacy caseload will move to Universal Credit during 2016 and 2017, claimants in receipt of Income based Employment and Support Allowance (ESA) will retain their current arrangements during this period unless there is a relevant change in their circumstances. Final decisions on the implementation of the programme will be informed by the development of the enhanced digital solution.</p>","Wirral West","Esther McVey","191507 ; 191509","2014-03-17T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/42619/answer","Biography information for Esther McVey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/42619/answer",,,,,"29",,,"2014-03-11",,"1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, whether claimants who begin claiming employment and support allowance prior to new claims being accepted by the Universal Credit system will be transferred to the universal credit system by the start of 2017 or end of 2017.","false","Biography information for Rachel Reeves","Leeds West","Rachel Reeves","191508"
